      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay but if you look at the actual data, it feels like people who argue for massive social spending regardless of the deficit are just being irresponsible with the future. dont u think it's kind of unrealistic to keep ignoring the debt just to fund these programs?",
      "source": "evaluator",
